{"tid":1686691,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"成班人幾個月口號叫錯哂","createTime":"2019-11-01T10:05:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T10:52:54.000Z","uid":239247,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b4d5e40610ff0868e003ee10ce922b46dccfe758","tid":1686691,"uid":239247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T10:05:13.000Z","msg":"試下唔好叫光復香港/時代革命<br />\n試下接既時候成句叫 <br />\n避免出現小圈子口號<br />\n行兩步已經叫緊唔同口號<br />\n同埋氣勢 一句細聲 第二句幾大聲都冇用<br />\n試下叫哂成句 傳到個個都叫同一句<br />\n同埋越大聲就越唔會怕醜 <br />\n好多人仲係怕醜仔唔敢叫/唔識？<br />\n夠大聲就清楚就越多人叫<br />\n所以聽日唔該各位<br />\n辛苦小小 叫口號成句叫<br />\n接既人都成句叫"},{"pid":"593e2f38aaf8b84fcbec028136e9042ed52a0c27","tid":1686691,"uid":2900,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T10:06:13.000Z","msg":"係 應該叫香港獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aed10c89b1b20aa3c64c19266c23edc289b80ed","tid":1686691,"uid":239247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T10:06:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a33cbc8429a3263f38167f33a4f097355698ca15","tid":1686691,"uid":285371,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T10:07:16.000Z","msg":"我覺得一句口號叫三次有效啲<br />\n第一次比人聽到<br />\n第二第三次啲人就會跟<br />\n香港人就係四個字max<br />\n講八個字會懶"},{"pid":"2d96d10422bfe7907d59edd6b8aeb9adfc7ea689","tid":1686691,"uid":239247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T10:07:22.000Z","msg":"叫咩都好 成句叫"},{"pid":"4ecbb4590b96c64221c77785d44c560799b2e6cd","tid":1686691,"uid":239247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T10:08:25.000Z","msg":"你不停轉口號點跟 <br />\n有啲人就係唔知幾時轉 唔敢叫"},{"pid":"9ca7126d90eeb2ed4985cf6c367a0b827e62b862","tid":1686691,"uid":239247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T10:08:50.000Z","msg":"出到黎仲懶乜鬼"},{"pid":"ca99fdf7b4126b171a849b7f68cb180ae8a25df7","tid":1686691,"uid":239247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T10:09:09.000Z","msg":"你地要叫比自己聽<br />\n番屋企叫呀"}